\caption{The measured EDM frequency shift $\eta_{\mathbf{B}}\cdot\Delta \omega_{EDM}$ for each of the 252 runs in the final (reduced) data set. Each run is plotted on either the top or bottom chart. Top: the frequency shifts measured between $\pm 6$ kV/cm. Bottom: shifts measured between $\pm 10$ kV/cm.}
